---
const highlights = [
  { icon: '🏔️', label: 'Mountain Views', desc: 'Surrounded by the Albanian Alps' },
  { icon: '🍽️', label: 'Home Cooking', desc: 'Traditional Albanian recipes' },
  { icon: '🤝', label: 'Family Run', desc: 'Personal care since 2012' },
];
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-subheading">A relaxing gateway</div>
    <h2 class="section-title about-heading">About Us</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="about-grid container">
    <!-- Left column: single image -->
    <div class="about-col-left">
      <img src="/image2.jpg" alt="Marashi Guesthouse exterior" loading="lazy" class="about-img" />
    </div>

    <!-- Right column: paragraph + image -->
    <div class="about-col-right">
      <div class="about-col-right-top">
        <img src="/photo1.jpg" alt="Mountain view from balcony" loading="lazy" class="about-img" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-col-right-bottom">
        <p class="about-desc">
          Founded in 2012 by the Marashi family, our guesthouse was born from a simple belief:
          every traveler deserves to feel like a welcomed guest, not just a customer. Nestled
          between ancient stone walls and pine-forested mountains, we invite you to slow down
          and experience Albania the way locals do.
        </p>
        <p class="about-desc">
          From handwoven textiles on the walls to the aroma of fresh burek each morning, every
          detail reflects generations of Albanian tradition. Our family takes pride in being
          your guide, your host, and your connection to this hidden gem of the Balkans.
        </p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn btn-primary">Who We Are</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--white);
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-heading {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: stretch;
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-col-left {
    height: 100%;
  }

  .about-col-right {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .about-col-right-top {
    flex: 1;
    max-height: 280px;
  }

  .about-col-right-bottom {
    flex: 2;
  }

  .about-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  /* Subheading */
  .about-subheading {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  /* Text */
  .about-desc {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 1.0rem;
  }

  .highlights {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .highlight-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--light);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .h-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .highlight-item strong {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .highlight-item p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .about-col-left {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .about-col-right-top {
      max-height: 200px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-col-left {
      height: 220px;
    }

    .about-col-right-top {
      max-height: 160px;
    }
  }
</style>
